name: Personality Prediction Using Facebook - A Neural Network Approach
tagline: A project for predicting personality of individuals using their facebook statistics. In this project we propose a neural network approach. We are doing this as our major project in 8th semester of B.Tech Computer Engg. at Jamia Millia Islamia in 2014
body:
### Authors and Contributors
This is B.Tech final year major project of Niyas C (@niyasc) and Akshay Kumar (@akshay061).
